Package fluent.ly

Class azzert

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.Assert
      • fluent.ly.azzert
  • public class azzert
extends org.junit.Assert
    Extends Assert with more assertion for equality comparisons. If the comparison yields a "not-equal" result, a JUnit assertion failure is issued.
    Author:
    Itay Maman Jul 9, 2007, Yossi Gil revised 2015-07-18
